CZR Remember there will always be sellers traders selling at everyresistance So there will be dips there you must watch volume bars when this happens to determine if sellers have enough strength behind them or if bulls will overtake them and breach that resistance If sellers winuse other indicators not sr levels that are further down to see if there is some temp support on dip that price might bounce off of if these dont hold expect dip to the next real sr level If these temp moving supports hold expect another attempt at breaching that resistance Remember price spends most of its time skirmishes trading between SR levels not at SR levels Whoever wins the skirmish bulls or bears will determine which way they will march to support or resistanceWhen the winner of skirmish arrives at support or resistance thats when the real battle begins front lines to win the war at support or resistance so they can gain ground and advance GLTAShow More
